Duties & responsibilities:

Handle daily operations and settlement of derivatives products;
Monitor client positions on wide range of products, including derivatives products;
Conduct margin calls and ensure all trades transacted comply with the credit control policies;
Participate in various system enhancements and projects implementation to meet business demands;
Night Shift required.

